snippet: LEAD: Once again the Democrats are tinkering with the Presidential nominating process, clearing the way for that behemoth of American politics, California, to move its 1992 primary from the very end of the primary season to nearly the beginning....
lead_paragraph: LEAD: Once again the Democrats are tinkering with the Presidential nominating process, clearing the way for that behemoth of American politics, California, to move its 1992 primary from the very end of the primary season to nearly the beginning.

headline.main: Political Memo;   Big State, Big Change, Big Risk for Democrats
